# Nishul Dhakar

I build end-to-end products from idea to production — frontend, backend, and AI systems.  
I own the full lifecycle: design, build, deploy, iterate. Focused on shipping real results.

Tech stack doesn't scare me. I learn whatever the project needs.

---

## Skills & Tools

- AI/LLM — LangChain, LangGraph, Groq, Gemini, Whisper, FLUX
- Backend — Python, FastAPI, Node.js, Next.js
- Frontend — React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Database — Supabase, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, MySQL
- Infra — DigitalOcean, Vercel, Railway, Render

